Program Description: Implementation of a stack to balance parenthesis, evaluate postfix expressions and transform infix expressions into postfix expressions.
                     Assignment for an algorithm class.
	

Author: Kulthum Lakha
	

Files: balancing.cpp - Main method to check whether an expression is balanced
	 infix2postfix.cpp - Main method to transform an infix expression into postfix
       input_balanced.txt - Test cases for balancing.cpp
       input_infix2postfix.txt - Test cases for infixtopostfix.cpp
       input_postfixEval.txt - Test cases for postfixEval.cpp
       postfixEval.cpp - Main method to evaluate postfix expressions
       stack.cpp - Stack implementation
       stack.hpp - Stack header file
	  
Compilation: $ g++ stack.cpp balancing.cpp
             $ g++ stack.cpp postfixEval.cpp
             $ g++ stack.cpp infixtopostfix.cpp
	             
Run: $ ./a.out
